quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vyanje n’ibihano bibabaza cane bimwe vy’akarorero
  15,51,Kandi ubabwire inkuru z’abashitsi b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  15,52,"Mugihe binjira munzu yiwe nukumuramutsa bavuze bati:- amahoro y’Imana abe kuri twese, nawe abishura nkuko nyene hanyuma aca avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabinuvye"
  15,53,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ntugire ubwoba twebwe tugufitiye inkuru nziza yuko uzokwibaruka ikibondo gifise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  15,54,"Nawe abishura ati:- munzaniye iyi nkuru mugihe namaze kuba umusaza, none n’iyihe nzira mumpaye y’izi nkuru nziza"
  15,55,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- tuguhaye iyi nkuru nziza y’ukuri, rero ntube mu bantu badebukirwa"
  15,56,"Nawe abishura ati:- ni nde adebukirwa kumigisha y’Umuremyi wiwe atari mu bantu bazimiye"
  15,57,"Yishura ati:- none ico mwipfuza n’igiki mwebwe mwatugendeye"
  15,58,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarungitswe kuri ba bantu bacumuye"
  15,59,"Dukuye mwo abakurikiye intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii), ntankeka twebwe tuzoba rokora uko bangana bose"
  15,60,"Dukuye mwo umukenyezi wiwe, niwe twibaza yuko yoba ari mu bantu bazo kwicara inyuma ya bose"
  15,61,"Izo ntumwa\tmugihe\tzashika\tku\tbantu b’intumwa\ty’Imana\tLutwi\t(iii) bafise ishusho ry’abantu"
  15,62,"Lutwi (iii) yavuze ati:- mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mu bantu mutazwi kandi nanje sindabazi"
  15,63,"Baca bishura bati:- twebwe tukuzaniye bimwe muvyo bahora bagirira ko amakenga"
  15,64,"Dushitse iwawe n’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi muba vugisha ukuri"
  15,65,"Rero nugende n’abantu bawe mugice c’ijoro nawe ubakurikire inyuma yanyu ntihagire umwe muri mwebwe ahindukira inyuma, hanyuma mugende mutumbera iyo mwategetswe kuja"
  15,66,Hanyuma tumucira intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) kuri rya jambo yuko imizi yabo izocibwa mugitondo
  15,67,Haca haza abantu bo mugisagara banezerewe
  15,68,"Intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yavuze iti:- mu vy’ukuri aba n’abashitsi banje ntimuntetereze"
  15,69,Kandi mutinye Imana yanyu ntimunkengere
  15,70,"Bavuga bati:- mbega twebwe ntitwakubujije kwakira abantu"
  15,71,"Yavuze ati:- aba bose n’abigeme banje nimwaba mwebwe muri mubagira ibikorwa"
  15,72,Ndarahiye k’ubuzima bwawe mu vy’ukuri abo bantu bari mububorerwe bwabo bataya taya hirya no hino
  15,73,Mumwanya ibihano biraba fata mugihe izuba ryaseruka
  15,74,"Hanyuma\tduca\ttugira\tivyo\tbisagara\tkuba\thasi\thejuru,\thanyuma tubashungurira imvura y’isegenya irimwo ivyondo vyo mumuriro udahera"
  15,75,"Mu vy’ukuri\tmuri ibi\tvyose harimwo icirwa ku bantu bapima\tibintu n’ibindi"
  15,76,N’ibi bisagara twahoneje biri munzira bacamwo mumwanya wose
  15,77,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo icirwa kubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  15,78,Mu vy’ukuri abantu bo mumashamba bari mubahemukiye imitima yabo
  15,79,"Kuri\tivyo\ttwarabahanye,\tn’ibi\tbisagara\tuko\tari\tbibiri\tvyari\tmunzira ziboneka neza"
  15,80,"Ntankeka\tabantu\tbo\tmugisagara\tc’Amabuye\tbarahakanye\tintumwa z’Imana"
  15,81,Twarabahaye impanuro zacu mugabo ntibazitaho
  15,82,Nabo bahora babaza amazu yabo ari mumisozi mumahoro ntangere
  15,83,Rero akaruru k’ibihano karabashikiye mugitondo cakare
  15,84,Ntaco vyabamariye muvyo bahora bagira
  15,85,"Natwe ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose atari uko ari ivy’ukuri,\tkandi\tntankeka\tumusi\tw’imperuka\tuzoshika,\trero\tnugire c’ikigongwe ciza kuwukugiriye inabi, impembo yanyu muzoyisanga k’umusi w’imperuka"
  15,86,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe muremyi wa vyose kandi niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije
  15,87,"Twaguhaye aya majambo y’Imana meranda uko ari indwi asomwa umwanya uwariwo wose, nukuguha iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ikwiye"
  15,88,"Ntukwege amaso yawe mukuraba muvyo twanejereje imirwi itandukanye yabo bansi b’Imana, kandi ntubagirire agahinda kandi wunamike ibaba ryawe ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  15,89,"Kandi uvuge uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi mubantu batuza mbonekana neza k’umugaragaro"
  15,90,Nkuko twabamanuriye ibihano bose tubitandukanije mumirwi n’iyindi
  15,91,Abagize iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu kuba ariryo koraniro ry’ububeshi
  15,92,"Nivyo, ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana yuko uko tuzoba baza abantu bose k’umusi w’imperuka"
  15,93,Kuvyo bahora bagira vyose
  15,94,"Rero bimenyeshe ivyo wategetswe kugira, kandi ube kure n’ibikorwa vyabagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  15,95,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\tturaguhagije\tmukugu\tkingira\tn’ivyo\tbafata minenerwe"
  15,96,"Abagira\tImana\thamwe\tn’izindi\tMana\tz’ibintazi,\trero\tubu\tvuba bazotahura neza"
  15,97,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turazi neza yuko igikiriza cawe cugarijwe n’ivyo bivugira
  15,98,"Nutakambire Umuremyi wawe hamwe n’ukuyihayaza, kandi ube muba yipfukamira bashize imitwe yabo hasi"
  15,99,"Kandi usenge Umuremyi wawe kugeza aho uzoshikirwa n’urupfu. Igisomwa c’Inzuki.\tIkigabane ca (14). Camanukiye IMakkat. Gifise imirongo"